title: DJ Mehdi: Made in France
overview: The story of the late DJ/producer DJ Mehdi, a young suburbanite of Tunisian origin who, during an early and extraordinary career, created the sound of the toughest collective in French rap and collaborated with the biggest names in rap in France and will subsequently become one of the most brilliant ambassadors of the "French Touch" internationally alongside Busy P, Cassius, Daft Punk, Justice and the Ed Banger label family.
